    - SORT  : To sort in an increasing order (str only)
  - Update template: 
    - Cisco
      - Cisco r1800, r1900, r2800, r2900, sw2940, sw2950, sw2960, sw3750
        sw3850, sw3650, swIE, rISR, asa
    - Wmware
    - esxi6
    - Huawei             
